parameters: \nc<Senpai>Good morning, Saki. I heard you went all out yesterday.

\nc<Senpai>Sorry, but let me speak first. Yesterday's recording has
been cancelled.

\nc<Senpai>It seems that Saki was too erotic, and it's not suitable for
broadcast. Even editing couldn't fix it.

\nc<Senpai>You should be glad, Saki. Thanks to being too erotic, you
were saved.
\nc<Senpai>Probably another staff member will end up recording it.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Sigh... I should be relieved, but somehow I feel guilty...
\nc<Senpai>Well, isn't it all good in the end?

\nc<Senpai>If we had really broadcasted a segment about barging into
rooms suddenly, it might have inspired copycats.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>But in the first place, you were the one who let it go on,
Senpai!
